creator: Akbr Umuziki
descriptionHtml:
Mp3 streaming Tracy Chapman made to fans easier by using the lyrics in it. An internet connection is required to use this app to listen songs.

Features :
~ Streaming Mp3
~ Info of Tracy Chapman
~ Lyrics with cool features.
~ Small memory Ram use.
~ Fanpage artist (FB,Twit).

Lyrics songs in this app:
+ Fast Car
+ Baby Can I Hold You
+ Give Me One Reason
+ The Promise
+ Behind the Wall
+ Crossroads
+ For My Lover
+ Across the Lines
+ Talkin' Bout a Revolution
+ Mountain O'Things
+ If Not Now
+ All That You Have Is Your Soul
+ Sing for You
+ Telling Stories
+ Unsung Psalm

This app is unofficial from an existing artist, created for Tracy Chapman fans. Hopefully this apps useful and as a lesson and entertainment for us all.

Thank you. Do not forget to comment, rate and share apps for fans among others.
